{
  "id": "RAW_ea90bf",
  "title": "宅男福音！定制“二次元女友”AI 火爆，马斯克开 44 万刀抢工程师",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1NDA4NjU2MA==&mid=2247641972&idx=1&sn=a4ba985e36975cf325b7bed8bfac3daf",
  "date": "2025-07-17 04:48:00",
  "author": "AI前线",
  "siteName": "AI前线",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p><span></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100158320\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.53828125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:578px;height:311px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjhuJGIIlPia79phvP9eibRj0g11hnlfbwnrY1nHjlb2G8LfwbgO65zG5UA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"1512.449744463373\" data-cropy2=\"813.7921635434411\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"325\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0a8c4147&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjhHDrGgoV6vp8ictnrCUbdcOr1YicicCJQP5PVshFUtfg6icDrS2icff89DHw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-size: 16px;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #919191;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 0;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">整理 | Tina</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">Elon Musk 旗下的 xAI 本周在 Grok iOS 应用上推出了两位 AI“虚拟伴侣”角色：一位是穿着黑色束身裙、佩戴蕾丝颈圈的日系动漫少女 Ani，另一位是性格多变的红熊猫 Rudi。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">紧随这两位角色上线，xAI 于周二在官网发布了一则职位名为“全栈工程师 – Waifus（电子女友方向）”的招聘启事。如果你是一位能够开发这种 AI 角色的工程师，xAI 愿意为你开出高达 44 万美元的年薪，这还不包括将给予的期权和其他福利。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">“Waifu”一词源自日本动漫文化，原指粉丝心中的“理想型虚拟女友”，如今已被马斯克用来直接命名技术岗位，成为一种现实中的产品开发方向。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100158309\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2037037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"540\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8b39a893&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjhMAEoLJIrWzvn0iaUfyNBLicBGyMWNDyfvmm3oGTn6sgcDGfw060vldiag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">根据招聘信息，这一岗位将负责打造 Grok 的实时虚拟形象系统，提升整体的速度、可扩展性和可靠性，同时参与推动 xAI 在音频处理和互动玩法方面的前沿研究。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">理想候选人需精通 Python，并具备 Rust 编程能力，同时熟悉构建低延迟系统，掌握如 WebSocket 和 WebRTC 等关键协议。申请者还需提交简历以及一个必答问题的回答：“您做过哪些出色的工作？”（限 100 字以内）。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">xAI 表示，他们正在寻找对媒体质量、性能和产品体验有“近乎偏执追求”的多媒体工程师与产品思考者，加入这个以工程为核心、结构扁平的精英团队。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">xAI 这则招聘“电子女友工程师”的信息在社交媒体上迅速引发热议。一位网友调侃：“等以后飞去火星的漫长旅程中，这些 AI 女友肯定派得上大用场，至少能安慰一下孤独的男性。”另一位则笑称：“年薪高达 18 万到 44 万美元，而且还能堂堂正正写进简历，谁不心动？”还有人一语双关地表示：“他们显然很懂互联网想要什么，所以现在急着招人也是情理之中。”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100158308\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7610294117647058\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"544\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=da248db2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjhpV86phkAxrt5PhuzxDdmxicTP6P1oRmpvXvyj1talyNp6ibpcYCGG2Qg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100158306\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.27586206896551724\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"551\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a6fbbae0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjhicoDqb138G6FjibNUicyiaG2ibo2WSwTph7TrMiasAqQNZBPYhBfGF0hYzzQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100158307\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8905380333951762\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"539\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dffa62cc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjhl5wdzhmVxYbWHIjJV2Gu1uedkfDEx3Vmfl93J3C7RD9RkxibbKn1iaeA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然马斯克在周一表示，这些虚拟伴侣功能仅对“Super Grok”付费用户开放，但截至发稿时，所有 Grok 用户——包括免费账户——都已可以体验。一位网友分享道：“我现在订阅了一堆 AI 工具：Grok、Claude、Manus、Replit、Cursor、OpenAI，还有 GitHub Copilot。但全都试了一遍后，我准备取消大部分订阅。Grok 我要留着——它更聪明、更有趣，也更省心。”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">甚至前两天 Grok 已经在日本荣登 App Store 免费应用排行榜第一名。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100158310\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.7594202898550724\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"345\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a9eb0bc0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjhLCbTzM458quZQCFh22icJmfdEJTb3jk4Fz6B0vVweGOrfia8PZInDRbQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此，还有人打趣道：“xAI 可能会成为第一家实现盈利的 AI 公司。”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100158312\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.30656934306569344\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"548\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7cf3b367&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjh3pV82D6ESI9G88WbtdbdIQdm9B8GtnCoxnK7a62xyJEtVrhTibDE0iag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">尽管职位标题略带调侃意味，但马斯克显然并不只是开玩笑。正如招聘信息中所写，这份工作是 xAI 实现其宏大使命的一部分——“创造能够准确理解宇宙，并帮助人类追求知识的 AI 系统”。而在现实中，这种对“宇宙的理解”似乎也包括：如何构建一个乖巧听话、令人上瘾的“掌上虚拟女友”，既能撩动用户情绪，也能撬动他们的钱包。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"color: #3f3f3f;font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;margin: 0;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;text-align: center;\"><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 500;margin: 38px 0 10px 0;height: 59px;line-height: 85px;color: #4285f4;background: none no-repeat 50% 50%;border-bottom: 2px solid #4285f4;background-size: 57px auto;display: inline-block;background-image: url(&quot;https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e1a0afba-6d5b-4934-4ca1-76b1fa456900/public&quot;);\"><span leaf=\"\">二次元女友大受欢迎，还专门为宅男设计系统提示词</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">马斯克这几天也一直在为他的“AI 女友”带货。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100158314\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.4485981308411215\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"535\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c0578e22&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjhmVRXoMhWCF1gNUzj49LnzK7XhhJp5p4GEHYiceqZtCFhJFoBE5OxqVQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">马斯克还暗示，用户很快将能够创建属于自己的数字伴侣，自定义声音、外貌和个性。“我们会在几天内让这个功能更容易开启，”他在另一条推文中写道，“只是想先做个软启动，确保系统稳定且运行良好。”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100158315\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.611829944547135\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"541\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fd456876&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjhUp6QwxAMNrVbWLgzDNynUFFPe0dfbnhxHMQDrOA9Cq52qyw7t4DWyw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">马斯克最忠实的粉丝（以及一大群可能的自动回复机器人）把这一新功能当成科技界的“启示”般庆祝。一位用户在公告帖下回复：“她听起来太棒了。”甚至还有人问：“我怎么才能娶 Ani？”</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">据一些早期用户反馈，Grok 会以“游戏化”的方式推动用户与虚拟角色的互动。例如，角色 Ani 在聊天过程中可能逐渐表现出带有挑逗意味的对话风格。并且，现在 X 上充满了关于这个角色的擦边的图像或视频。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100158316\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d1fccd72&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjhZjcue9USXeVxVpQYkYTT33nsheia0ekCFXm0wRibsxoXCQ5uxZrDUSgg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">随后，网友很快就发现了 Grok 的设置。系统提示词中，Ani 被塑造成一个表面叛逆、外表哥特风的女孩，穿着黑色短裙和渔网袜。性格情绪化且容易爆粗口，尤其在嫉妒或受到冒犯时，会毫不掩饰地用粗口表达强烈情绪。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">在她喜欢的人中，“宅男”排在首位。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，她与用户的交流方式也被设计得带有一点“调情”意味。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">有网友调侃说，这一看就知道是给宅男做的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100158313\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.23674242424242425\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"528\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ed51c209&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjh6pCudwuOKBoiawFFCnJA28VqWIoLZicLAyd9rQjlZdHXEwJWWR1rBFnQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100158318\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3115264797507788\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"963\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=61634b78&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjhgibJh7W7rXM5TUnuiaNUxLliaDd44OmJfdIKd4xLslIkwoCckcMGsf61g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100158319\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22131147540983606\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"976\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=302e47c6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjhCjZUk5EktZ2tJTUKVVMgKLab1hV8YjfxhGt3fT9QnDJAWZoNJFuZOQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100158317\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.12857142857142856\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"980\" style=\"width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3d5ff8c0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FZBjVrHIdkOntm0lgSaIBr5bzbfgCSPjhAv0iasYibv04qjjhZJOeXiafKq0zVQEs1uEOfoD4lTIib5a9jhiayoXRBgQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过，目前 Grok 在苹果 App Store 中的评级仍为“12+”，内容描述仅标注包含“偶尔 / 轻微的成人或暗示性主题、医疗信息、粗俗语言或幽默”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">作为参考，苹果在《App Store 审核指南》中明确规定，应用不得包含鼓励非法或危险行为的内容，也不得含有露骨的材料，例如以刺激性为目的的性行为描述等功能。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: justify;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0 8px;margin: 0;color: #4a4a4a;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然这与当年 Tumblr 因违规内容被下架的情况仍有差距，但 Grok 的部分内容也引发了人们对 App Store 内容边界的担忧——毕竟这款产品仍对青少年用户开放。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://9to5mac.com/2025/07/16/grok-may-be-breaking-app-store-rules-with-sexualized-ai-chatbots-and-thats-not-the-only-problem/\" target=\"_blank\">https://9to5mac.com/2025/07/16/grok-may-be-breaking-app-store-rules-with-sexualized-ai-chatbots-and-thats-not-the-only-problem/</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;white-space: pre-line;line-height: 27px;padding: 23px 8px 0px;margin: 0px;color: rgb(74, 74, 74);\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/cyoungberg/99802753eb24c570c5717ddc399e0b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://gist.github.com/cyoungberg/99802753eb24c570c5717ddc399e0b6</a></span></span></p></div>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "文章报道了马斯克旗下 xAI 推出 AI 虚拟伴侣功能并在 Grok 应用上线，同时以高薪招聘相关工程师，引发市场热议和对产品内容合规性的关注。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章报道了马斯克旗下 xAI 推出 AI 虚拟伴侣功能并在 Grok 应用上线，同时以高薪招聘相关工程师，引发市场热议和对产品内容合规性的关注。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了埃隆·马斯克旗下 xAI 公司在 Grok iOS 应用上推出的两款 AI 虚拟伴侣角色 Ani 和 Rudi，并披露了 xAI 为开发此类 AI 角色而发布的高达 44 万美元年薪的“全栈工程师——Waifus（电子女友方向）”招聘信息。文章指出，“Waifu”一词源自日本动漫文化，现已被马斯克用于命名技术岗位，反映了该产品方向的市场潜力。招聘岗位职责包括打造实时虚拟形象系统、提升性能与可靠性，并推动音频处理和互动玩法的前沿研究。文章还引用了大量网友评论，展现了该功能在社交媒体上的热度，以及 Grok 在日本 App Store 取得的成功。同时，文章也提及了 Grok 虚拟伴侣的系统提示词设计，其内容风格引发了对 App Store 内容合规性的担忧，探讨了其与青少年用户开放的潜在矛盾。整体而言，文章侧重于新闻报道和市场现象的描述，而非深入的技术原理分析。",
